OL,3,CChannel Islands' visitors frustrated
OL,4,Cat flight and ferry delays
OL,6,FVisitors have voiced their
OL,7,Ffrustrations following delays and
OL,8,Fcancellations travelling by sea and
OL,9,Fair to and from the .
OL,11,FIt comes as ferry operator announced
OL,12,Fthe cancellation of some of its June
OL,13,Fsailings because of 10 days of strikes
OL,14,Fby French port workers.
OL,16,FAirlines and are also currently
OL,17,Foperating with fewer planes due to
OL,18,Fmechanical and operational issues
OL,19,Fwhich are having a knock-on effect on
OL,20,Fschedules.
