OL,3,CChannel Islands' visitors frustrated
OL,4,Cat flight and ferry delays
OL,6,FPenny and Derrick Wood have travelled
OL,7,Fto Jersey from Norfolk for their
OL,8,Fwedding anniversary but their ferry
OL,9,Fservice was moved from Portsmouth to
OL,10,FPoole and eventually cancelled due to
OL,11,Fbad weather.
OL,13,FPenny says: "It's cost us an overnight
OL,14,Fin Portsmouth, an extra night at our
OL,15,Fhotel and we've spent a whole day on a
OL,16,Fboat which we hadn't planned.
OL,18,F"It's a shame really. It must affect
OL,19,Fyour (Jersey) tourism. If you're
OL,20,Fpaying for something, you expect to
OL,21,Fget what you pay for."
