OL,6,FCondor has apologised for the schedule
OL,7,Fchanges but stated it is out of their
OL,8,Fcontrol because of the strike action.
OL,10,FAir travel has also faced disruption.
OL,12,FOne passenger at Guernsey Airport told
OL,13,FITV News: "I've just come back from a
OL,14,Fbusiness trip and had nine flights.
OL,15,FThe only flight that was cancelled was
OL,16,FAurigny on the way back which really
OL,17,Fspoilt the whole thing."
