OL,6,FAnother says: "I think it's a shame
OL,7,Fbecause I was hoping to visit my
OL,8,Fsister via East Midlands and that
OL,9,Fservice has been cancelled, so it's a
OL,10,Fbit of a disappointment."
OL,12,FAurigny recently had to because of an
OL,13,Faircraft shortage.
OL,15,FThe company has now announced that one
OL,16,Fof its ATR72 aircraft will return to
OL,17,Fservice next week, meaning the airline
OL,18,Fwill operate with four planes.
