OL,6,FWhile running a reduced schedule, a
OL,7,FSAAB 340 aircraft will continue to be
OL,8,Fused for backup until Thursday 4 July
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FNico Bezuidenhout, Chief Executive
OL,12,FOfficer at Aurigny, adds: "Customers
OL,13,Fare reminded that they will be
OL,14,Fcontacted proactively by email if
OL,15,Ftheir flights are affected by the
OL,16,Freduced schedule during June.
