OL,6,F"Any flight delayed beyond three hours
OL,7,Fand flights that have been rebooked to
OL,8,Fa different airport, will be eligible
OL,9,Ffor free changes without fare
OL,10,Fdifferences to an alternative and
OL,11,Fsuitable date, or passengers can opt
OL,12,Ffor a refund."
