OL,6,FShe explains: "You never really know
OL,7,Fif it's going to be on time, or if
OL,8,Fyou're going to get where you need to
OL,9,Fbe on time.
OL,11,F"I know my brother was over recently
OL,12,Fand they got delayed for a day so they
OL,13,Fhad to come a day later. It creates a
OL,14,Flot of complications."
